{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["The Cloudy Mask\n\n<size=45>Chapter 5: The Truth, Pt. 1<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Gneisenau's Room","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_room","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I somehow managed to drag Deutschland out of her room and decided to ask her Iron Blood comrades about the situation.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I had a feeling this would happen eventually, and it seems my hunch was correct.","actor":404020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I'm sorry, Deutschland. But please believe me when I say nobody meant to hurt you.","actor":404020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"You expect me to believe that?","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.1,"number":3,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":403040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Oh, right... You don't know the story behind all this, Commander.","actor":404020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"That being the case, I'll call over the girls relevant to this discussion and tell them about this. You and Deutschland can sit in the next room over and listen.","actor":404020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":2,"say":"Port - Dormitory Salon","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Thank you for coming, Eugen, Spee, Tirpitz, and Z1. I have something to tell you.","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It's about... Deutschland, isn't it?","actor":403050,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Correct. A long time ago, we all entered an agreement to go along with her egotistic tendencies so she could live a happy life.","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I'm sure you all remember this, yes?","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"They what?! I can't just sit here and listen to this...!","dir":1,"side":2,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Hold Deutschland back before she storms out of the room."}],"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":403040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Let go of me!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":22.5}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":403040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"... She bit my arm.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Stop it, you insubordinate, lowly animal...!","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Mrgh... Gah...!","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Yeah, I remember that... I've grown used to her attitude by now, so I don't really need to be bound by that agreement anymore.","actor":403030,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I know it's for her sake, but it's a fact that what we've done isn't right.","actor":405020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Indeed. It's also caused trouble for other people. Furthermore, Deutschland knows about it now, and she feels really hurt by it.","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That is why I've called you here - so we can discuss what to do next.","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"......","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"They'll just keep making a fool of me. I know they will.","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"(Whispering) Slave... what should I do...?","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.4,"number":2,"x":22.5}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":403040,"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"DEYIZHI5","fadeOut":1.5}